# CARL Commands Domain
# ====================
# Star-commands for quick presales actions.

COMMANDS_RULE_0=*checklist - Run the full estimation gap checklist against all artefacts in claude-artefacts/ and estimates/. Verify: requirement coverage, effort reasonableness, assumption consistency, missing categories (PM, QA, DevOps, migration, training, docs, UAT, warranty, environments)
COMMANDS_RULE_1=*recap - Read all artefacts in claude-artefacts/, initial_questions/, and estimates/ and summarize: phases completed, open questions count, gaps found, orphan line items, overall confidence level
COMMANDS_RULE_2=*benchmark <query> - Search claude-mem for historical effort data matching the query, then check benchmarks/ directory for reference ranges. Present results as a comparison table.
